'''沃兹杀亲案'''（{{lang-en|Watts family murders}}）是于2018年8月13日发生在[[美国|美国]][[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[弗雷德里克_(科罗拉多州)|弗雷德里克]]的一起[[伦常命案|伦常命案]]，罪犯克里斯托弗·李·沃兹[[窒息|勒死]]孕妻珊南·凯瑟琳·沃茨后，用毯子闷死了四岁女儿贝拉和三岁女儿克勒斯蒂。2018年11月6日，法庭裁定沃兹犯多项[[谋杀|一级谋杀罪]]，但考虑到沃兹有认罪，将处罚从[[死刑|死刑]]改成监禁。沃兹被判五项{{tsl|en|Life imprisonment in the United States|美国终身监禁|终身监禁}}刑期，不得假释，其中三项刑期[[量刑|连续服刑]]，两项同时服刑。

== 背景 ==
克里斯托弗·李·沃兹（Christopher Lee Watts）和珊南·凯瑟琳·沃茨（Shan'ann Cathryn Watts）分别是[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]{{tsl|en|Spring Lake, North Carolina|春湖 (北卡罗来纳州)|春湖}}和{{tsl|en|Aberdeen, North Carolina|阿伯丁 (北卡罗来纳州)|阿伯丁}}生人。根据网络记录，两人于2010年结识，2012年11月3日在北卡罗来纳州[[梅克倫堡縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|梅克倫堡縣]]结婚<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://heavy.com/news/2018/08/chris-watts-shanann-watts-husband/|title=Chris Watts: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|publisher={{tsl|en|Heavy.com||Heavy}}|language=en|date=2018-08-16|access-date=2019-06-01|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816080352/https://heavy.com/news/2018/08/chris-watts-shanann-watts-husband/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大女儿叫贝拉·玛丽·沃兹（Bella Marie Watts，2013年12月17日出生），小女儿叫克勒斯蒂·凯瑟琳·“茜茜”·沃兹（Celeste Cathryn "Cece" Watts，2015年7月17日）。一家人住在2013年购买的一间五居室房子里<ref name="Coloradoan 23 August">{{cite news |author1=Sady Swanson |title=Christopher Watts and Shannnon Watts: Their friends saw a 'perfect' family. What happened? |url=https://www.coloradoan.com/story/news/2018/08/23/colorado-watts-family-who-were-christopher-watts-shannon-watts-prior-murder/1062614002/ |accessdate=2019-02-02|work={{tsl|en|Fort Collins Coloradoan||Fort Collins Coloradoan}}|date=2018-08-23 |publisher=USA Today Network}}</ref>。2015年，夫妇俩宣告破产<ref name=CBSNews>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/shanann-watts-frederick-colorado-family-struggled-with-finances-before-chris-watts-allegedly-killed-pregnant-wife-kids-2018-08-17/|title=Colorado family struggled with finances before man allegedly killed pregnant wife, kids|publisher=[[CBS新聞|CBS News]]|language=en|date=2018-08-17|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330234552/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/shanann-watts-frederick-colorado-family-struggled-with-finances-before-chris-watts-allegedly-killed-pregnant-wife-kids-2018-08-17/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。克里斯任职于{{tsl|en|Anadarko Petroleum|阿纳达科石油公司}}，珊南则是[[多層次傳銷|多層次傳銷]]公司Le-Vel的独立代表<ref>{{cite news|author1=Kathleen Foody|author2=Jonathan Drew|title=Colorado man arrested as hunt for family leads to body of pregnant wife, possible remains of young daughters|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/world/slain-colorado-mother-painted-rosy-picture-of-married-life|accessdate=2019-02-02|work=[[国家邮报|National Post]]|publisher=Postmedia Network Inc.|date=2018-08-17|location=[[弗雷德里克_(科罗拉多州)|Frederick, Colorado]]|archive-date=2021-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210922230434/https://nationalpost.com/news/world/slain-colorado-mother-painted-rosy-picture-of-married-life|dead-url=no}}</ref>，负责销售一款名叫Thrive的产品<ref name=CBSNews/>。珊南遇害时已经怀孕15周，夫妇俩给胎中的儿子取名为尼克·李·沃兹（Niko Lee Watts）<ref name=netflix>{{cite web |title=American Murder: The Family Next Door {{!}} Netflix Official Site |url=https://www.netflix.com/title/81130130 |website=www.netflix.com |accessdate=2020-09-25 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407221944/https://www.netflix.com/title/81130130 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 失踪==
2018年8月13日，凌晨1点48分，珊南从[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]出差回来，由同事妮可·乌托夫特·阿特金森（Nickole Utoft Atkinson）载回家，当时克里斯和两个女儿在家<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/crime/shanann-chris-watts-family-murder-timeline/|title=Mom & Kids Vanish, Husband Pleads for Help – Then 3 Bodies Turn Up: How Watts Murder Case Unfolded|website=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]|language=en|access-date=2019-02-02|author=Helling, Steve|date=2018-09-18|archive-date=2019-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817075631/https://people.com/crime/shanann-chris-watts-family-murder-timeline/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当天晚些时候，阿特金森发短信提醒珊南按照约定去做[[婦產科學|产检]]，但没有人回应，阿特金森随向警方报告珊南和两个女孩失踪。珊南错过当天公司的会议后，阿特金森于中午12点10分来到沃兹家<ref>{{cite news|author1=Annelene Oberholzer|title=Man arrested for killing his pregnant wife and daughters, days after pleading for their return|url=https://www.news24.com/World/News/man-arrested-for-killing-his-pregnant-wife-and-daughters-days-after-pleading-for-their-return-20180817|accessdate=2019-02-02|publisher={{tsl|en|News24||News24}}|location=[[開普敦|Cape Town]]|date=2018-08-17|archive-date=2019-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817075628/https://www.news24.com/World/News/man-arrested-for-killing-his-pregnant-wife-and-daughters-days-after-pleading-for-their-return-20180817|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Amelia McDonell-Parry |title=Colorado Man Claims He Killed Pregnant Wife After She Strangled Their Daughters |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-news/colorado-man-claims-he-killed-pregnant-wife-after-she-strangled-kids-713675/ |accessdate=2019-02-02 |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |date=2018-08-21 |archive-date=2019-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817075630/https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-news/colorado-man-claims-he-killed-pregnant-wife-after-she-strangled-kids-713675/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿特金森按了门铃、敲了门，但没人回应。阿特金森认为克里斯在上班，于是打电话叫来了弗雷德里克消防局。下午1点40分，一名工作人员前来做健康检查.<ref>{{cite news |title=Chris Watts case: Everything to know so far about the alleged murders of his wife, daughters |url=https://www.cbs46.com/archives/chris-watts-case-everything-to-know-so-far-about-the/article_85542398-e7da-5510-ba1d-f3baf7e6449a.html |accessdate=2019-02-02 |publisher={{tsl|en|WGCL-TV||WGCL-TV}} |date=2018-08-17 |location=[[亚特兰大|Atlanta]] |archive-date=2019-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817075633/https://www.cbs46.com/archives/chris-watts-case-everything-to-know-so-far-about-the/article_85542398-e7da-5510-ba1d-f3baf7e6449a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。克里斯已经在家，还和工作人员讲了一些寻找失踪家人的办法<ref>{{cite news|title=Video: Police interview Chris Watts after he murdered his family|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cYhfJDIzifE|accessdate=2019-02-02|work=[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]]|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2018-12-03|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216100109/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cYhfJDIzifE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。检查期间，克里斯同意警察搜查住所，没有找到珊农和女孩们的踪迹，但找到了珊南的钱包，里面装着手机和钥匙。而珊南的车子就停在车库，还装着女孩们的婴儿车。珊南的婚戒在主人床上<ref>{{cite news |author1=Sady Swanson |title=Timeline: Key dates in investigation of deaths of Shannon Watts, two daughters in Colorado |url=https://www.coloradoan.com/story/news/2018/08/21/timeline-investigation-christopher-watts-colorado-family-killing-shannon-watts/1043602002/ |accessdate=2019-02-02|work=Fort Collins Coloradoan |publisher=USA Today Network |date=2018-08-21 }}</ref>。

[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]和{{tsl|en|Colorado Bureau of Investigation|科罗拉多州调查局}}次日联合进行调查。最初克里斯告诉警方，自己不知道妻子和女儿在那里，说自从13号凌晨5点15分出门上班起，就没见过妻子<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|last=WTVD|date=2020-01-16|title=Shanann Watts' family denounces upcoming Lifetime movie about daughter's murder|url=https://abc11.com/5855171/|access-date=2020-08-04|website=ABC11 Raleigh-Durham|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116171106/https://abc11.com/5855171/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[丹佛|丹佛]]电视台{{tsl|en|KMGH-TV|KMGH-TV}}和{{tsl|en|KUSA-TV|KUSA-TV}}前来采访，克里斯在家门外接受访问时，恳求她们回家。采访期间房子内传出侦查人员和[[警犬|警犬]]的叫声<ref>{{cite news |author1=Rob Low |title=The scent of death: Police dogs and the Chris Watts investigation |url=https://kdvr.com/2018/08/17/the-scent-of-death-police-dogs-and-the-chris-watts-investigation/ |publisher={{tsl|en|KDVR||KDVR}} |date=2018-08-17 |location=[[丹佛|Denver, Colorado]] |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2019-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817075628/https://kdvr.com/2018/08/17/the-scent-of-death-police-dogs-and-the-chris-watts-investigation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Blair Miller |title=Chris Watts murder case: Everything we know so far about the deaths of his wife, daughters |url=https://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/chris-watts-case/chris-watts-murder-case-everything-we-know-so-far-about-the-deaths-of-his-wife-daughters |publisher={{tsl|en|KMGH-TV||KMGH-TV}} |date=2018-08-21 |location=Frederick, Colorado |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2018-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180822020613/https://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/chris-watts-case/chris-watts-murder-case-everything-we-know-so-far-about-the-deaths-of-his-wife-daughters |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

