=== 逮捕和起诉 ===
沃兹后来于2018年8月15日被问讯调查。根据问讯[[宣誓书|宣誓书]]，沃兹没有通过[[测谎仪|测谎仪]]测试后，承认自己杀害了珊南。在认罪前，沃兹将自己犯罪的经过告诉父亲。审讯中，沃兹说妻子曾跟他提出分居，但他不同意，于是她勒死两个女儿，他怒火中烧勒死了她。之后，他将遗体搬到了他工作的地方，一个偏远的储油站<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://abc13.com/chris-watts-wife-killed-our-girls-so-i-strangled-her/4009246/|title=Chris Watts: Wife killed our girls, so I strangled her|date=2018-08-20|publisher={{tsl|en|KTRK-TV||KTRK-TV}}|location=[[休斯敦|Houston]]|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021041821/https://abc13.com/chris-watts-wife-killed-our-girls-so-i-strangled-her/4009246/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

8月16日，在沃兹前东家阿纳达科石油公司的帮助下，警方找到了沃兹家人的遗体。其中他两个女儿的遗体藏在油罐里，妻子的遗体埋在附近的浅坑中。沃兹被捕当天就遭公司开除<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.coloradoan.com/story/news/2018/11/19/chris-watts-sentenced-3-consecutive-life-terms-killing-family-shannon-watts-christopher/2017606002/|title=Christopher Watts will serve 3 life sentences for murdering wife Shannon, 2 daughters|website=Fort Collins Coloradoan|language=en|access-date=2019-02-02|author=Swanson, Sady Swanson; Coltrain, Nick}}</ref>。

8月21日，沃兹被控五项[[谋杀|一级谋杀罪]]，包括针对两个孩子各一项的“杀害未满12岁的孩子且被告人处于可信状态”、一项{{tsl|en|Foeticide|杀胎|非法终止妊娠}}及三项{{tsl|en|disposal of human corpses|弃置人类遗体|糟蹋逝者遗体}}<ref>{{cite news |author1=Madison Park |title=Chris Watts case: What we learned from unsealed affidavit |url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/20/us/chris-watts-investigation-affidavit/index.html |publisher=[[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] |agency=Cable News Network |date=2018-08-20 |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411042131/https://www.cnn.com/2018/08/20/us/chris-watts-investigation-affidavit/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首次庭审驳回保释申请。后来的听证会上，沃兹的保释金定为500万美元，若要释放要缴纳15%。9月1日，他缴纳75万美元，临时获释，等待法律诉讼<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/chris-watts-case/chris-watts-waives-preliminary-hearing-in-court-appearance-will-be-held-without-bond |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010195858/https://www.thedenverchannel.com/news/chris-watts-case/chris-watts-waives-preliminary-hearing-in-court-appearance-will-be-held-without-bond |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

媒体认为此案为[[伦常命案|伦常命案]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/people-kill-close-relatives-explaining-family-annihilators/story?id=57305463|title=When people kill close relatives: Explaining 'family annihilators'|date=2018-08-21|publisher=[[ABC新聞|ABC News]]|language=en|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-date=2019-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925030153/https://abcnews.go.com/US/people-kill-close-relatives-explaining-family-annihilators/story?id=57305463|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于此类案件在开学前的8月份较为多发，侦查工作可能会有所拖延<ref>{{cite news |last= |first 1= |author1=Emily Shapiro |title=When people kill close relatives: Explaining 'family annihilators' |url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/people-kill-close-relatives-explaining-family-annihilators/story?id=57305463 |publisher=ABC News |date=2018-08-21 |accessdate=2020-10-10 |archive-date=2019-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925030153/https://abcnews.go.com/US/people-kill-close-relatives-explaining-family-annihilators/story?id=57305463 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前联邦调查局[[罪犯側寫|罪犯側寫]]员{{tsl|en|Candice DeLong|坎迪丝·德隆}}指出，沃兹案之类的案件非常少见，一般伦常命案的凶手会在{{tsl|en|murder–suicide|杀人后自杀|杀人后自杀}}<ref>{{cite web |title=‘Chris Watts Is What We Call A Family Annihilator,’ Says Former FBI Criminal Profiles |url=https://www.drphil.com/videos/chris-watts-is-what-we-call-a-family-annihilator-says-former-fbi-criminal-profiles/ |website={{tsl|en|Dr. Phil (talk show)||Dr. Phil}} |accessdate=2019-02-02 |archive-date=2020-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409220117/https://www.drphil.com/videos/chris-watts-is-what-we-call-a-family-annihilator-says-former-fbi-criminal-profiles/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，考虑到对自己杀人的行为抱有负罪感，而作出的行动<ref>{{cite web |last1=Harfenist |first1=Ethan |title=Chris Watts Says He Contemplated Suicide After Murdering His Wife And Two Daughters |url=https://www.oxygen.com/crime-time/chris-watts-says-he-contemplated-suicide-after-murders-Shanna-bell-celeste |website=Oxygen |access-date=2019-04-02 |date=2019-03-08 |archive-date=2020-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409220123/https://www.oxygen.com/crime-time/chris-watts-says-he-contemplated-suicide-after-murders-Shanna-bell-celeste |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在接受《{{tsl|en|Dr. Phil (talk show)|菲尔博士|菲尔博士}}》采访时，沃兹律师透露，他承认自己是在与珊南争论离婚的事情后杀了她。杀人期间，贝拉走了进来。他告诉贝拉，珊南不过是病了。杀人后，沃兹将珊南的遗体和女孩们锁进他上班用的卡车的后备箱。沃兹用放在那里的一条毯子闷死了两个女孩，当时女孩们没有坐儿童座椅<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wral.com/dr-phil-exclusive-chris-watts-confession-and-his-daughter-s-final-words/18235411/|title=Dr. Phil exclusive: Chris Watts' confession and his daughter's final words|date=2019-03-05|website=WRAL.com|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190305181134/https://www.wral.com/dr-phil-exclusive-chris-watts-confession-and-his-daughter-s-final-words/18235411/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 认罪协议和量刑 ===
11月6日，沃兹正式承认杀人。考虑到珊南的家人不希望再有人死，[[地方检察官|地方检察官]]没有提出[[死刑|死刑]]。死者家人也接受认罪的决定。11月19日，沃兹被判五项终身监禁，不得假释，其中三项刑期[[量刑|连续服刑]]，两项同时服刑，另外因非法终止珊南妊娠获48年额外刑期，因糟蹋逝者遗体获36年额外刑期。法庭撤销了他的500万美元保释金，立即将其还押<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/colorado-dad-christopher-watts-sentenced-life-prison-killing-his-pregnant-n937931|title=Christopher Watts sentenced to life in prison without parole for killing his pregnant wife and young daughters|last=Burke|first=Minyvonne|publisher=[[NBC新聞|NBC News]]|date=2018-11-19|accessdate=2018-11-19|archive-date=2019-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107005850/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/colorado-dad-christopher-watts-sentenced-life-prison-killing-his-pregnant-n937931|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/11/19/us/colorado-chris-watts-sentencing/index.html|title=Chris Watts sentenced to life for 'inhumane' killings of two daughters and pregnant wife|publisher=CNN|author1=McLaughlin, Eliott C.|author2=Murray, Kelly|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426105934/https://www.cnn.com/2018/11/19/us/colorado-chris-watts-sentencing/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年12月3日，出于“安全考虑”，沃兹被转移到州外的地点<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://radaronline.com/exclusives/2018/12/chris-watts-moved-prison-safety-concerns-killing-murder-pregnant-wife-shannan-watts-daughters-life-sentence/|title=Killer Chris Watts Moved To Unknown Prison Due To 'Safety Concerns'|date=2018-12-14|website={{tsl|en|RadarOnline||RadarOnline}}|access-date=2019-02-02|author=Hatziefstathiou, Nik|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520100822/https://radaronline.com/exclusives/2018/12/chris-watts-moved-prison-safety-concerns-killing-murder-pregnant-wife-shannan-watts-daughters-life-sentence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月5日，沃兹抵达{{tsl|en|Dodge Correctional Institution|道奇惩教所}}，[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]]{{tsl|en|Waupun, Wisconsin|沃邦 (威斯康星州)|沃邦}}的一座{{tsl|en|maximum-security prison|最高设防监狱}}，继续服完余下刑期<ref>{{Cite web|author=Hatziefstathiou, Nik|url=https://radaronline.com/exclusives/2018/12/chris-watts-wisconsin-prison-life-sentence-murder-colorado-killer/|title=Final Rotting Place: Chris Watts Arrives At Wisconsin Prison To Serve Life Sentence|date=2018-12-05|website=RadarOnline|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-date=2019-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125113926/https://radaronline.com/exclusives/2018/12/chris-watts-wisconsin-prison-life-sentence-murder-colorado-killer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=NBC15 Investigates: Inmate transfer process, Chris Watts confirmed in WI|url=https://www.nbc15.com/content/news/Chris-Watts-serving-sentence-in-Waupun-prison-502782471.html|accessdate=2019-02-02|publisher={{tsl|en|WMTV||WMTV}}|date=2018-12-14|author=Anderson, Hannah|location=[[麦迪逊|Madison, Wisconsin]]|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406213707/https://www.nbc15.com/content/news/Chris-Watts-serving-sentence-in-Waupun-prison-502782471.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

